My city where I be, can't change it, See them walk, see them talk that language. Hard denim louis belt still hanging, wear a flag but I but I ain't bangin. 305 the way I ride, the way I vibe I love it everyday outside and I can't lie the sunny skies the hunnies right, the money's right. I came from the bottom of the beaca, and got hard as I got older, they say I started with some sand then I shook it to a boulder and thats how I handle business. im just tryna reach my quota.
